<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>text-shadow and box-shadow</title>
    <style>
        h1{
            text-shadow: 5px 5px red;
        }
        div{
            width: 200px;
            background-color: brown;
            border: 2px solid green;
            box-shadow: 30px -15px teal;
            /* box-shadow: inset 30px -15px teal; */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>siyam</h1>
    <div>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Aut iusto, sint nam sed explicabo fugit itaque, in magnam accusamus esse, neque consectetur aliquid error? Quidem aliquid quaerat minus dolor laudantium!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
